,Recommended,227580,19479421,"Posted: 4 December, 2015",all,robert,"A fantastic puzzle game, 10,000,000 thrives on the ability to hop right back in after a crushing defeat. Your ultimate goal is to secure a score of 10,000,000, finally being able to escape from the clutches of a castle that you've been locked away in. Various upgrades are also available, in which you can boost your various attacks, as well as creating special potions with fantastic, and maybe some not so fantastic perks.My only complaint is that it still is, at its heart, a mobile game. Nevertheless, the $5 dollar price tag still provides hours of fun, especially if you're aiming at earning all of the achievements the game has to offer, even if some of them are a bit tedious.If you're a die-hard puzzle game lover, buy this game immediately. If not, check the game out on a sale.8.7/10"
