,Recommended,227580,16912982,"Posted: 6 July, 2015",all,Voiced,"Achievement completion at time of writing: 100%This is a port of the mobile game of the same name. It is a match 3 game where you either slide a row or a column to make matches for whatever is needed at the time. Locked Doors and Chests require keys, Monsters require Swords and Staves, Shields are used for defense, Stars for items to help, and Stone and Wood for building your home base afterwards.The objective is to go as far as you can in a dungeon, and upon failure you take all the resources you gathered to upgrade your home base to allow even further runs. The main goal is to have a total score of over 10,000,000 in one run of a dungeon.It's fun for a few hours, though the game is pretty short. If you can get it cheap, it'll be good value."
