,Recommended,227580,13750885,"Posted: 31 December, 2014",all,ShakespearOnIce,"A relatively simple match-3 style game where you match tiles to execute various commands while adventuring through a linear dungeon hallway: attack, block, magic, get item, use key (for doors and treasure chests), and a few resource gathering things. Get cash, XP, and resources, upgrade your character, and repeat. Get a score of 10,000,000 to beat the game. Nowhere near as forgiving as something like Bejeweled, but the hallway really just boils down to a timer mechanic that forces you to match certain types of tiles in order to add time to your game.Worth skipping a soda with lunch to buy, but not enough here to recommend further."
