76561197981356193,Recommended,227580,896851,"Posted: 10 April, 2013",all,fatcoland,"This game is a big slide puzzle that has an ever changing picture.  It may sound complicated and overwhelming at first, but it really isn't that hard by any means.  You slide squares on an x/y axis to make three-in-a-row matches vertically and horizontally.  Depending on what you have matched up has a specific effect as to what happens to your adventurer.  Combining swords or wands will make your adventurer attack enemies that stand before him.  Combining shields and treasure chests will grant the adventurer bonuses to help him last longer.  Bigger combos make for bigger points, and your goal is to break the coveted 10,000,000 mark in one game.  If you like slide puzzle games, you'll find yourself playing this casual game for awhile."
