76561198013197255,Recommended,227580,26464608,"Posted: 6 November, 2016",all,JayKay,"A rather simple match-3 with simple Rogue ""lite"" elements and a simple plot, Notice the pattern yet?You awake in a stone chamber with a bunch of doors, all but one is locked off, entering the big door causes the game to begin. The game follows a runner format type of game, up top is your dude running from left to right, he'll run until he hits a obstacle (Monster or a lock) and you match what you need from the bottom puzzle board.Sword & staves do damage while the keys unlock locks, also in the board are armor tiles, item tiles and resource tiles. You keep this up until you lose by the screen catching up with you, which then causes you to awake back in the stone chamber.You can spend the resources you find to open and upgrade the rooms which in turn boost your abillity to play the game,rinse & repeat until you get 10,000,000 score and you win the game, simple.There are milestones and challenges to complete that give you some resources and multipliers adding your end goal.All in all it's a short but addicting match-3, nothing amazing but simply solid in its execution."
